Quest:Amber Tomb

From Wizard101 Wiki
Jump to: navigation, search

Quest Information


Prequest:
Strange Allies

Given By: Queen Sabina

Giver Location: Moon Cliffs
This is a storyline quest.

Goals:
Defeat Goliath Stingers and

Collect Venom (in Stinger Cave)

Talk to Queen Sabina
Hand In: Queen Sabina

Reward:

450
46,490


Leads to:

Unstuck in Time

Quest Dialogue


This page is for recording a complete Quest Dialogue of all the conversation and story during a quest.
This includes NPC discussions, Narrator statements, and Creature speeches.


Documentation on how to edit this page can be found at Template:QuestInfobox/doc.

Hints, guides, and discussions of the Wiki content related to Amber Tomb should be placed in the Wiki Page Discussion Forums.

Search for content related to Amber Tomb in the Central Wiki Forums by clicking here.
